```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> LoadingImage: Open(path/stdin)
  LoadingImage --> ShowingImage: First render ready
  ShowingImage --> OcrRunning: Spawn OCR job
  OcrRunning --> OcrReady: OCR results arrive
  OcrReady --> Selecting: User drag-selects text
  Selecting --> OcrReady: Selection cleared
  ShowingImage --> Closed: Space/Esc
  OcrRunning --> Closed: Space/Esc (cancel/ignore)
  OcrReady --> Closed: Space/Esc
  Closed --> [*]
```
